PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773144740
OL,3,CMental health charity secures funding
OL,4,Cto repair storm-damaged building
OL,6,FRunning three bases across South
OL,7,FShore, Bispham, and Cleveleys, CITC
OL,8,Foffers therapy to around 160 children,
OL,9,Fadults and families every week, with
OL,10,Fsessions starting from just #5.
OL,12,FBut the hub was forced into an
OL,13,Femergency closure in October 2025
OL,14,Fafter extreme weather caused extensive
OL,15,Fwater damage, destroying ceilings,
OL,16,Fwalls, and floors.
OL,18,FThe damage left more than 100
OL,19,Fvulnerable people at risk of losing
OL,20,Faccess to their regular therapy
OL,21,Fsessions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773144740
OL,3,CMental health charity secures funding
OL,4,Cto repair storm-damaged building
OL,6,FThe funding comes from the
OL,7,Fgovernment's Pride of Place Impact
OL,8,FFund, which targets investment toward
OL,9,Fthe UK's most deprived communities.
OL,11,FStuart Hutton-Brown, CEO and Founder
OL,12,Fof CITC, said: "Without this money, we
OL,13,Fwouldn't have been able to open our
OL,14,FWaterloo Hub again."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773144740
OL,3,CMental health charity secures funding
OL,4,Cto repair storm-damaged building
OL,6,FHe continued to say: "Now, instead of
OL,7,F100 people needing support from GPs or
OL,8,FA&E or otherwise, they can continue to
OL,9,Fbe supported by the professionals and
OL,10,Fvolunteers who they've already been
OL,11,Fbuilding trusted relationships with
OL,12,Fhere."
OL,14,FWhen the site reopens the hub will
OL,15,Ffeature a new sensory room, improved
OL,16,Fdisability accessibility, two
OL,17,Fadditional counselling suites and a
OL,18,Fnew shared community space.
OL,26,@nD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
