PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773144740
OL,3,CMental health charity secures funding
OL,4,Cto repair storm-damaged building
OL,6,FMP for Blackpool South Chris Webb,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The charity's absence has been
OL,8,Ffelt keenly by the community. This
OL,9,Ffunding not only restores what was
OL,10,Flost but secures the building for the
OL,11,Fcharity's future."
OL,13,FThe Waterloo Road hub is expected to
OL,14,Fwelcome its first clients back through
OL,15,Fthe doors in the coming months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
